  <Docs>
    <summary>Describes the component swizzle for a Vulkan YCbCr conversion.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`GRVkYcbcrComponents` specifies which Vulkan image component (R, G, B, or A) maps to each channel when performing YCbCr color conversion. Use this struct when configuring a <xref:SkiaSharp.GrVkYcbcrConversionInfo> for a Vulkan backend surface that uses a YCbCr format.

This is a value type; no disposal is required.

## Examples

```csharp
var components = new GRVkYcbcrComponents
{
    R = 0, // VK_COMPONENT_SWIZZLE_IDENTITY
    G = 0,
    B = 0,
    A = 0
};
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
